2. Titan level

This Medusa level requires both of the guaranteed scrolls of earth from
Sokoban, but there are enough boulders available to compensate up to 3
traceless sinking boulders. Though the necessary number of boulders can
also in this case be further reduced by using a spare charge from a wand
of cold and choosing a slightly different path over the sea. This level
has some specifics to mention; the secret door top-left on the map has to
be kicked down to have the necessary room to push the boulders away from
the blocking wall. Take also care that you don't push any boulder to the
right wall, because of the water squares in the lower part of the room you
would waste a boulder. Finally many of the walls of the ruins in the middle
of the map will have to be broke down using some mandatory means of digging
to be able to build that path.

